# Integrity Guard Logic Template

When generating L2 integration tests for HiveMind, you MUST include a logic probe for the following entities:

{% if entity_type == 'Task' %}
1. Verify `(Task {status: 'done'})-[:PRODUCED]->(Result)` exists in Neo4j.
2. Verify PG record has a valid `output_vfs_path`.
3. Check `integrity_prober.py --id {{ entity_id }}` for logical drift.
{% elif entity_type == 'Document' %}
1. Verify `(Doc)-[:HAS_CHUNKS]->(Chunk)` exists.
2. Verify VectorStore has records for all chunk IDs.
{% endif %}

Acceptance: All cross-database invariants must pass before the integration test is considered 'GREEN'.
